            <note xml:id="foot.f4">CD cited William Elliot on the wild boar in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> 1: 267. See letters from <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1495.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Walter Elliot</ref>, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6856.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">7 August 1869</ref> and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6880.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">7 September 1869</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f5">CD refers to <hi rend="italic">Land and Water</hi>; see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6887.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Edward Blyth, 13 September 1869</ref>.</note>
